headline: How Is Gen Digital's Stock Performance Compared to Other Software - Infrastructure Stocks?
summary: Although Gen Digital has outpaced its industry peers over the past year, Wall Street analysts maintain a cautiously optimistic outlook on the stock’s prospects.
